// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4132 — Mass File Rename (sarcoma)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 20472baf-6cf5-523d-81d6-31417a7b0497

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
